@startuml
title analysis.agreement - Inter-tool agreement
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "agreement.py\npython -m analysis.agreement" as ag
file "analysis_out/dataset_long.csv" as long
file "analysis_out/agreement.csv" as out

long --> ag : read long dataset
ag --> out : write agreement pairs\n(Spearman rho + n_common)

note right of ag
Scope:
- inter-tool + intra-metric only
- default min_common=2
end note

@enduml
